Definition: an eastern Christian in Egypt or Syria who adheres to the Orthodox faith as defined by the council of Chalcedon in 451 and as accepted by the Byzantine emperor
Synonyms: Melchite, Christian, an, eastern, in, Egypt, or, Syria, who, adheres, to, the, Orthodox, faith, as, defined, by, council, of, Chalcedon, and, accepted, Byzantine, emperor
Category: noun.person
